## 2. API 文档规范

### OpenAPI 3.0 规范

```yaml
# ✅ Good: openapi.yaml
openapi: 3.1.0
info:
  title: G-Zang 交易服务 API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: |
    G-Zang 财务管理系统的交易服务 API。

    ## 认证
    所有接口需要在 Header 中携带 JWT Token：
    ```
    Authorization: Bearer <token>
    ```

    ## 错误处理
    所有错误响应遵循统一格式：
    ```json
    {
      "code": "ERROR_CODE",
      "message": "用户友好的错误描述",
      "data": null,
      "timestamp": 1711545600000
    }
    ```

paths:
  /api/transactions:
    post:
      summary: 创建交易记录
      description: 创建一条新的交易记录（收入、支出或转账）。
      operationId: createTransaction
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateTransactionRequest'
            examples:
              支出记录:
                value:
                  type: 2
                  amount: 150.50
                  categoryId: 10
                  accountId: 1
                  remark: 午餐
      responses:
        '201':
          description: 创建成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TransactionResponse'
        '400':
          description: 请求参数错误
        '401':
          description: 未认证
        '403':
          description: 无权限

components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT

  schemas:
    CreateTransactionRequest:
      type: object
      required:
        - type
        - amount
        - categoryId
        - accountId
        - happenTime
      properties:
        type:
          type: integer
          enum: [1, 2, 3]
          description: 交易类型：1=收入，2=支出，3=转账
        amount:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          minimum: 0.01
        categoryId:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        accountId:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        remark:
          type: string
          maxLength: 500
        happenTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time

    TransactionResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        type:
          type: integer
        amount:
          type: number
          format: decimal
        categoryName:
          type: string
        accountName:
          type: string
        remark:
          type: string
        happenTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time

    ErrorResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
        data:
          type: object
          nullable: true
        timestamp:
          type: integer
          format: int64
```

