## 3. 变更日志规范

```markdown
# Changelog
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/).

## [1.2.0] - 2026-03-27
### Added
- `feat(transaction)`: 支持语音输入创建交易记录 (#456)
- `feat(report)`: 新增月度趋势图表组件

### Changed
- `refactor(auth)`: 重构 Token 刷新逻辑，解决并发竞态问题
- `perf(transaction)`: 优化交易列表查询，添加复合索引

### Fixed
- `fix(auth)`: 修复多次登录导致 Session 泄漏问题

### Security
- `security`: 升级 Spring Boot 版本，修复 CVE-2026-1234

## [1.1.0] - 2026-02-15
### Added
- 初始版本功能
